{"tid":1525194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］東涌東薈城擴建部份開幕","createTime":"2019-08-31T20:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T20:22:13.000Z","uid":266169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b61e8821aa4164ebce70ced85068d354b2d4e2a","tid":1525194,"uid":266169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:21:20.000Z","msg":"全港最大型的名牌折扣商場東薈城名店倉擴建部份現已試業。商場樓高7層，擴建後雲集高達150 個國際品牌，全年提供低至1折的折扣優惠。至於，最受東涌居民關注美食廣場「食代館」位於7樓，而UA戲院亦即將開幕。為慶祝全新東薈城名店倉閃亮登場，商場將會即日至9月1日期間推出一連串以「全新型格 暢遊盛夏」為題的推廣活動，顧客憑指定消費更可專享精彩購物禮遇。<br />\n<br />\n東薈城名店倉擴建後食肆數量亦翻倍至超過30間，以滿足東涌居民對餐飲需求。當中美食廣場「食代館」佔地9,000平方呎，裝演富有本土情懷，配上傳統特色建築竹棚及水磨石等，設計有心思。其他食肆包括：六小館、洪師父台灣牛肉麵、春水堂人文茶館、牛角次男坊、元氣壽司、一風堂、Outback Steakhouse、樂天皇朝等。<br />\n<br />\n參加互動遊戲觸碰水果贏取冷壓菠蘿汁<br />\n<br />\n活動期間的週六及日(8月24-25日、8月31日、 9月1日 )，商場二樓天橋同時特設「炎夏消暑樂園」，讓顧客參加互動遊戲贏取飲品。顧客只要驅動單車，扭動方向盤觸碰水果，獲取指定分數，便可免費獲得「bless」冷壓菠蘿汁一支，清新涼快過盛夏。凡在商場任何餐飲商戶單次消費滿港幣300元或以上，即可登記參加遊戲一次。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2431442/%E6%9D%B1%E8%96%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%90%8D%E5%BA%97%E5%80%89%E6%93%B4%E5%BB%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A9%A6%E6%A5%AD!%20%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%96%E9%96%93LINE%20FRIENDS%20Store%20outlet%E9%96%8B%E5%B9%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2431442%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%2596%2588%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2580%2589%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E6%25A5%25AD%21%2520%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2596%2593LINE%2520FRIENDS%2520Store%2520outlet%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B9%2595&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=cb90e07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2431442/%E6%9D%B1%E8%96%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%90%8D%E5%BA%97%E5%80%89%E6%93%B4%E5%BB%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A9%A6%E6%A5%AD!%20%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%96%E9%96%93LINE%20FRIENDS%20Store%20outlet%E9%96%8B%E5%B9%95</a><br />\n<br />\n好似好吸引 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e337cc4cdb6d811c11281603d0a0f11b98d3c033","tid":1525194,"uid":266169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:22:02.000Z","msg":"吖屌 開錯台"},{"pid":"d57b97765453b29401f52c01400f811a22ba727d","tid":1525194,"uid":209242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:22:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>全民跳閘運動</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，可唔可以應承我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrYA42t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrYA42t.png&h=cb3f89f7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}